  res %>% 
  filter(
    hoslem_test > 0.01,
    harrell_c > 0.83
  ) %>% 
  mutate(
    calibrated = ifelse(hoslem_test > 0.05, "Calibrated", "Non-calibrated"),
    hoslem_test = round(hoslem_test, 3),
    harrell_c = round(harrell_c, 3)
  )
